Hi, guys! Today I prepared the MOST POPULAR FOOD of KFC! KFC’s Fried Chicken, Tenders, and Crispy Chicken Sandwich(Zinger Burger) and newly released Fried Chicken Cartilage Bites! To enjoy the KFC’s popular menus, I also brought the various dipping sauces which are Emmental Cheese Fondue Sauce, Cheddar Cheese Sauce, Sweet Chili Sauce! I was really surprised by such a thick patty in the burger! Also, it was so tasty to eat the burger with cheddar cheese sauce! The Fried Chicken Cartilages, which I tried for the first time, were spicy and really crispy! They felt like chips and something special! KFC’s Fried chickens are spicy and salty, and it’s one of the fast foods that often come to my mind because of that! I think Tenders and Fried Chickens are much tastier with the dipping sauces! I could enjoy KFC’s menus due to a variety of sauces! Thank you for watching my video today!
